Mass is a basic property of matter.", "fibs": ["fermi"]}
{"text": "It does not depend on the temperature, pressure or location of the object in space.", "fibs": ["temperature"]}
{"text": "The SI unit of mass is kilogram (kg).", "fibs": ["SI"]}
{"text": "The prototypes of the International  standard kilogram supplied by the International Bureau of Weights and Measures (BIPM) are available in many other laboratories of different countries.", "fibs": ["kilogram"]}
{"text": "While dealing with atoms and molecules, the kilogram is an inconvenient unit.", "fibs": ["kilogram"]}
